The API that is built into the microCMS is intended to be small and easy to extend.
As of now, it includes:

Database
 - confirm_query
 - query
 - fetch_assoc
 - fetch_array
 - rows
 - prep_data
 
Core
 - redirect_to
 - verifyEmail
 -- Pending
  --- set_admin
  --- log_timer
  --- check_version

Sentry
 - get_real_ip
 - ip_location
 - check_ban
 - ban_ip
